sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP SDK
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP | 8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Driver as KFP Driver v2<br/>(in pipeline pod)
    participant Launcher as KFP Launcher v2<br/>(in pipeline pod)
    participant S3 as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/443/TCP
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-service<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MW as Metadata Writer
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over User, MW: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP | Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>DB Protocol | Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store compiled pipeline<br/>HTTP/HTTPS | AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP | SA Token

    K8s->>Argo: Workflow CR created
    Argo->>K8s: Create pipeline task pods

    Note over K8s, Cache: Flow 3: Step Caching Check
    K8s->>Cache: Mutating webhook (pod creation)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP | TLS
    Cache->>DB: Check cache hit<br/>DB Protocol | Username/Password
    Cache-->>K8s: Modify pod spec (cached/uncached)

    Driver->>API: Resolve inputs, get task spec<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP | SA Token
    Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS | AccessKey/SecretKey

    Note over Launcher: Execute user container

    Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS | AccessKey/SecretKey
    Launcher->>MLMD: Log execution metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP | plaintext

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP | SA Token
    PA->>API: Report execution status<br/>HTTP/gRPC 8888/8887/TCP | SA Token

    MW->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP | SA Token
    MW->>MLMD: Write execution metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP | plaintext

    Note over User, MW: Flow 2: Scheduled/Recurring Run

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP | Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP | SA Token

    loop On cron/periodic schedule
        Note over K8s: SWF Controller watches CRs
        K8s->>K8s: SWF Controller creates Workflow CR
        K8s->>Argo: New Workflow CR triggers execution
    end
